  <title>GDPR</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">GDPR</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">In accordance with the new European GDPR privacy legislation, here is the EC Software and HM Forum privacy policy. We&apos;re including the full text for your information, although only the forum portions (which are slightly more detailed in this version) are really relevant here. Basically, all we need to do to comply with the new regulations is describe what we have already been doing since we started. We have never collected any personal information on the forum, never performed tracking and never passed any information on to any other parties. For example, we have always refused to provide addresses of customers as references to other customers on request. </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="text-strong" style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">1. INTRODUCTION</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">EC Software is committed to protecting your privacy. We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to others. Our website is structured so that you can visit and download trial software without identifying yourself or revealing any personal information.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">If you choose to provide us personally identifiable information (any information by which you can be identified), you can be assured that it will only be used to support your customer relationship with EC Software.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">In accordance with the new European GDPR privacy legislation, here is the EC Software and HM Forum privacy policy. We&apos;re including the full text for your information, although only the forum portions (which are slightly more detailed in this version) are really relevant here. Basically, all we need to do to comply with the new regulations is describe what we have already been doing since we started. We have never collected any personal information on the forum, never performed tracking and never passed any information on to any other parties. For example, we have always refused to provide addresses of customers as references to other customers on request. We used to have Google Analytics installed for statistics on forum access but didn&apos;t ever do much with it. Now we have removed that also, because the potential privacy issues of using it far outweighed the tiny benefits of having it.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"></para>
